            div.row
                div.text-content.six.columns
                    h3 What is a hackathon?
                    p A hackathon is a weekend long event where students from all 
                      | majors can develop a project (like an app or website) with
                      | the best resources and mentors to learn.
                div.text-content.six.columns
                    h3 Who can attend?
                    p Any student, high school - grad school may participate. Others
                      | who wish to be involved may come and mentor. Minors are encouraged
                      | to attend, but they must email us (fashtechhack@kent.edu) for a 
                      | waiver to sign before the event.
            div.row
