                    h3 How much does this cost?
                    p Nothing! The Fashion / Tech Hackathon is free for all to attend.
                      | We''ll provide your meals and swag for the weekend, and in
                      | some cases we'll even provide travel reimbursement up to $150.
                div.text-content.six.columns
